git cloning: 	
git clone https://github.com/deepshigaravee/CM26EC002-ecommerce-notes.git

…or create a new repository on the command line
echo "# CM26EC002-ecommerce-notes" >> README.md
git init
git add README.md
git commit -m "first commit"
git branch -M main
git remote add origin https://github.com/deepshigaravee/CM26EC002-ecommerce-notes.git
git push -u origin main
…or push an existing repository from the command line
git remote add origin https://github.com/deepshigaravee/CM26EC002-ecommerce-notes.git
git branch -M main
git push -u origin main
